orknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/7773/1-Tui_on_Poor_Knights_Lily.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/7773/1-Tui_on_Poor_Knights_Lily.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\">A closeup showing the seeds which later will drop after the flower dies and dries.<a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0002/2634/Poor_Knights_lily_Xeronema_callistemon-2.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0002/2634/Poor_Knights_lily_Xeronema_callistemon-2.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a><br><br>The dried seed head (Late January)<br><a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0011/3143/1-Xeronema_callistemon_seed_head.__.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0011/3143/1-Xeronema_callistemon_seed_head.__.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a><br><br>A closeup of the seed capsules just before falling.<br><a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0011/3148/1-Xeronema_callistemon_seed_head.__-001.__-001.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0011/3148/1-Xeronema_callistemon_seed_head.__-001.__-001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a><br><br>Thanks to Wikipedia for text and Information: <a style=\"font-size: 1em;\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/\" target=\"_blank\">http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/</a></p> <p> </p> <br style=\"clear:both;\"> <div class=\"hr\"> </div> ",
